Chinese people for long time affected by sunzi saying: you can always win if you know others and youself.&nbsp;<div><br></div><div>It is smart. It's considered as wisdom. It is remembered in deep heart as if the proverbs.&nbsp;</div><div><br></div><div>Chinese philosophy love to took people as enemies - watch their every activities, steal every info in order to know them. At the same time, compare them with himself.&nbsp;</div><div><br></div><div>Once they feel confident. They begin to defeat them. The kindnesses is pretended. The smile is pretended. The love is pretended. The help is limited and pretended. The whole person is pretended. Nothing is true.&nbsp;</div><div><br></div><div>All they want from bottom of heart is to win others. Hate others. Curse others. Destroy others. Kill others. The more knowledge they have the more authentic they can pretended. I grew up in such fresh.&nbsp;</div><div><br></div><div><br></div><div>Jesus is opposite to Chinese philosophy - He is willing to lose in world stead of win.&nbsp;</div><div><br></div><div>To lose become a joy because of Him.&nbsp;</div><div><br></div><div><br></div><div><br></div><div><br></div><div><br></div><div><br></div><div><br></div>